title: Tuesday Pt1: Bills crush Titans; Eagles dominate Vikings; Josh Allen and Tua's development
itunes:title: Tuesday Pt1: Bills crush Titans; Eagles dominate Vikings; Josh Allen and Tua's development
description:
Part One of the Good Morning Football Podcast begins with Hosts Jamie Erdahl, Kyle Brandt, Peter Schrager, and Super Bowl Champion Jason McCourty reacting to the Buffalo Bills crushing the Tennessee Titans and the Philadelphia Eagles dominating the Minnesota Vikings. Later, they’re joined by Scott Pioli and he talks about the development of Josh Allen and Tua Tagovailoa and the unlikely comeback by the New York Jets.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
